    "attributes": {
        "action": "Post on Motorway message boards to remind middle lane 'Hoggers' to Pull Over",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "Every driver has experienced being in a long tail back as one lorry slowly edges past another. \r\n\r\nDrivers can now be given 3 points for not pulling back into the Left-hand lane but this is not enforced. \r\n\r\nWhy not use the Electronic signs to remind drivers to use the left to improve traffic flow?",
